title: Ebro In The Morning - Release Your Wiggle + Cruise Ship Brawl

itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 7/1/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio discussing the brawl on the Carnival Cruise, Beyonce's album release date, and so much more!

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!

Subscribe to "Summer Jam: Through The Years" - hosted by Laura Stylez!
